title: The Long Swift Sword of Siegfried (1971, Something Weird Video)
description:
In days of yore, Sigfried. a bold and handsome young knight, battles villains and fire breathing dragons, all for king, country, and the love of a fair maiden. On his quest for a wife, the brave and virile knight plunges his long swift sword again and again, to relieve his manly tensions. Finally, he sets his sights on a beautiful princess, Kriemhild. Has the great conqueror met his match?

A glorious tail of Jousting, jubilation, and jugs from the Knight of Naughtiness, David F. Friedman. 

A super early role for Sybil Danning - here credited as Sybelle Danninger!!!
